entries.quest_location_d: Travel to the Dathomir system and follow the patrol navigation waypoints. As you reach one navigation waypoint, you will get a new waypoint to the next location on the patrol route.
entries.quest_patrol_d: When you reach a navigation waypoint you will receive a new one to the next location. Follow the patrol waypoints until you come to the end of your patrol.
entries.split_quest_alert: Alert! Unauthorized vessel suspected of smuggling attempting to leave system. Detain vessel and inspect its contents.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Patrol the Dathomir System
entries.title_d: The Inquisition has been alerted to higher levels of unauthorized activity in the Dathomir system. They want to find out what this activity is and who is behind it. You are to patrol the Dathomir system and keep your eyes open for any suspicious activity.
